	dprr:hasNoteText "Praef. Soc. 216. See MRR 1.251. As Marius is a praenomen, he should be indexed with the Statilii. (RS, CP)\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1396> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1396" ;
