	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "In command under Paullus of Lucanian allies (Liv. 22.42.4-6, and 43.7). For the anecdote showing how Fabius kept his loyalty, see Val. Max. 7.3.7; Frontin. Str. 4.7.36; Plut. Fab. 20; Auct. Vir. Ill. 43.5; cf. on Marcellus and Bantius, Liv. 23.15; Plut. Marc. 10; Dio fr. 57.33)." .
